  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK572">
<l>kaṇṇōṭṭat tuḷḷa tulakiya laḵtilā </l>
<l>ruṇmai nilakkup poṟai</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The prosperity of the world springs from the kindliness, the existence of those who have no (kindliness) is a burden to the earth.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
